# --- Evidence policy ---
# evidence는 커밋 대상(SSOT)이라 전체 ignore 금지.
# 다만 대형 바이너리가 생기면 개별 확장자만 제외.
evidence/**/*.png
evidence/**/*.mp4
evidence/**/*.zip

# Storybook build output
# Evidence generated outputs
evidence/**/actual/
evidence/**/summary.json
evidence/**/output.txt

# Storybook build output
storybook-static/
full_evidence_run.err

